OL,6,FMeanwhile, parents and families have
OL,7,Ftold ITV News they've had to pull
OL,8,Ftheir children out of mainstream state
OL,9,Fschools for months on end due to
OL,10,Finadequate provision.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIn autumn this year, the Education
OL,18,FSecretary, Bridget Phillipson, will
OL,19,Foutline her plans for reforming Send
OL,20,F(Special Educational Needs and
OL,21,FDisabilities) provisions.
