OL,3,CUnease among Labour MPs as government
OL,4,Ceyes reforms to Send provisions
OL,6,FIn recent weeks, government ministers
OL,7,Fhave refused to rule out scrapping
OL,8,FEducation, Health and Care Plans
OL,9,F(EHCPs) - the legal document outlining
OL,10,Fsupport for Send children.
OL,12,FThe speculation has fuelled suspicion
OL,13,Fand anger among campaigners and parent
OL,14,Fgroups, who over the weekend penned an
OL,15,Fopen letter urging the government not
OL,16,Fto remove the legal rights of Send
OL,17,Fchildren.
