OL,3,CUnease among Labour MPs as government
OL,4,Ceyes reforms to Send provisions
OL,6,FBut there are now growing concerns
OL,7,Famong Labour MPs about what these
OL,8,Fchanges could look like and how they
OL,9,Fwill sell reforms on the doorstep.
OL,11,FOne backbencher told ITV News that
OL,12,Fministers needed to frame the changes
OL,13,Fin the context of improving outcomes
OL,14,Ffor children rather than cost-cutting.
OL,16,F"This is the same issue as with winter
OL,17,Ffuel and welfare - there's too much of
OL,18,Fa focus on making the numbers work on
OL,19,Fa spreadsheet without thinking about
OL,20,Fthe impact on people," they said.
