OL,6,F"If people think the government is
OL,7,Fscrapping EHCPs as another form of
OL,8,Fpenny-pinching ` that's going to be a
OL,9,Fhard sell," another Labour MP said.
OL,11,FJen Craft, Labour MP for Thurrock and
OL,12,Fa Send parent, told ITV News that
OL,13,Fspecial educational needs is one of
OL,14,Fthe "biggest issues" in her inbox. She
OL,15,Fdescribes the government's upcoming
OL,16,Freforms as an "opportunity" to reform
OL,17,Fan "adversarial" and "broken" system.
OL,19,FBut she warned that any changes needed
OL,20,Fto be done in collaboration with
OL,21,Ffamilies.
