OL,6,F"EHCPs aren't a golden solution, and
OL,7,Fthe system does need reform ` but
OL,8,Fwe've got to explain what is being
OL,9,Fdone and bring parents on side,"
OL,10,Fanother backbencher said.
OL,12,FOver the summer, ministers will
OL,13,Fcontinue discussions with MPs and
OL,14,Fcampaigners before confirming plans in
OL,15,Fthe School's White Paper.
